      • customizeConnection

        protected void customizeConnection​(HttpURLConnection connection)
        Hook method which allows subclasses to easily customize the connections created by executeGet(String) and executePost(String, String) - for example, setting a custom read timeout or request header.

        This implementation is a no-op.

        Parameters:
        connection - The connection to customize.
